==Details==
===Description=== The [[Underground]] is unlocked when you purchase the [[Explorer Kit]] located in Cinnabar Island Shop. It also has its own currency called [[Diamonds]] that can be used to purchase upgrades for the [[Underground]] or [[Masterball]] at the Pokémon League. For more information about the [[Underground]], open the mines after you purchased the [[Explorer Kit]] and click on the ''Help'' tab.
